{"tid":93568,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【你願意嗎？】韓生物複製趨商業化　70萬可「復活」愛犬","createTime":"2017-01-24T13:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T10:04:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d576aa2c481ec65f6c28e0a5e3600803bd24827","tid":93568,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:41:56.000Z","msg":"【橙訊】「複製羊多利」在上世紀90年代被複製成功後，全球科學家均努力研究其他動物的複製技術，甚至發展成一門生意。其中韓國Sooam生物技術研究基金會自2006年起推出寵物複製服務，雖然每次服務高達10萬美元(約合港元77.6萬)，但顧客仍然絡繹不絕。<br />\n<br />\n自06年起，Sooam基金會受個人或國家機構委託，複製頂級嗅探犬及搜救犬，已成功了將近800隻。個人客戶也不乏王子、名人和億萬富翁，診所複製出的寵物能夠完美代替他們之前的愛寵，真正實現讓寵物陪伴一生的夢想。<br />\n<br />\n「這些人和自己的寵物都有著深厚的感情，比起傳統方法讓寵物自然逝去然後懷念它們，複製提供了另外一種心理上的選擇」。基金會研究員兼發言人王在雄(Wang Jae-Woong)說，「複製技術，給你一個讓寵物起死回生的機會。」<br />\n<br />\n基金會最廣為人知的狗類複製，是對前警犬特拉克(Trakr)的複製。它在美國「9&middot;11」恐襲中搜救出最後一名生還者，被認為是世界「最值得複製的狗」。基金會此後複製出的5只特拉克都繼續擔任搜救犬工作。<br />\n<br />\n此外，基金會還多次向國家申請研究人類幹細胞，但都被拒絕。不過他們同時亦嘗試複製其他物種，包括早已滅絕的猛獁象。Sooam團隊就曾試圖從猛獁象的冷凍遺骸中培育活細胞，預計這一計劃需時數十年。"},{"pid":"7274e033717da8aa0aba0bc068eadd437b5b32bf","tid":93568,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:44:28.000Z","msg":"客戶來自全球　多複製「優秀」搜救和警犬<br />\n<br />\n在公司一個牆壁上展示了多張來自世界各地成功複製的犬隻照片，當中包括在美國九一一恐襲中搜救了最後一名生還者的英雄拯救犬Trakr。Trakr在2009年以14歲的高齡去世（狗1歲相當於人類7歲），牠的基因由SOOAM複製成功，當年新聞曾在美國報道引來話題。Tarkr的「後代」現正在美國生活，繼續擔任搜救犬工作。<br />\n<br />\n「一隻優秀的搜救犬需要有靈敏的嗅覺與高度的集中力。」首爾市內在去年4月設立了一間名為「四季犬隻訓練所」，專門用作訓練複製搜救犬的訓練場。其中一名訓練員說道：「牠們比一般犬隻優秀得多。」SOOAM公司近年接下了來自中國、美國、俄羅斯、甚至阿聯酋的訂單，複製警犬或搜救犬，以「延續優秀犬隻基因」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/600/10/10/64/10106431_952343.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F600%2F10%2F10%2F64%2F10106431_952343.png&h=a0cf2f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「莉菲」真的是莉菲嗎？<br />\n<br />\n生物複製往往存在極大的道德爭議問題。有人覺得複製生命是「對神的褻瀆」，有違天理。然而也有人認為複製技術可以為人類解構生命之源帶來更大啟示，技術可以為人類社會帶來更大裨益。黃禹錫屬於後者，他表示設立SOOAM的目的是：「複製優秀犬隻的基因，為社會作出貢獻，生物複製的時代應當來臨。」<br />\n<br />\n生物複製仍然有太多值得商榷的東西。基因雖是一致，但個體並不一致：一對孖生兄弟有相同的基因，但並不代表兩人是同一個人。被複製出來的「莉菲」，會是當年與比利一家生活多年的莉菲嗎？相信「莉菲」在第一眼看見比利抱起牠的時候，腦中只會想着：「這是哪位？」。利用生物複製「延續愛犬的性命」，或許只是人類強加在寵物身上的感情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/600/10/10/64/10106430_257881.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F600%2F10%2F10%2F64%2F10106430_257881.png&h=d35be8b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2017/01/23/010049350.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2017%2F01%2F23%2F010049350.shtml&d=qyCkgQ%2FcYzJgaAoU1GnSSxpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=b670a096\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2017/01/23/010049350.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"d0b02a92e703a7e7652d1ba94c1383691f7dac82","tid":93568,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:49:44.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4557f424bb7a405d4e8bb73a887701a81e5952","tid":93568,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:51:02.000Z","msg":"非100%成功　可致代母犬流產甚至死亡<br />\n<br />\n而且複製並非100%成功，當年黃禹錫實驗的3000多顆受精卵中，只有3顆成功長成胚胎，並只有1顆成功誕生成為「史納比」。今天成功率雖已提高不少，但SOOAM也直言「無法保證必然成功」，而複製需利用真實的母犬懷胎產子，或會為犬隻帶來痛苦。<br />\n<br />\n中國《百科知識》雜誌副總編、前醫學科學院醫學信息研究所研究員張田勘表示，複製失敗的情況或會導致母犬流產甚至死亡，把實驗加諸在犬隻身上違反倫理道德，因此並不認為技術可以真正普及。日本東北大學動物生殖科學種村健太郎教授亦表示：「即使已累積了一定的實驗次數，老鼠亦只有約10%的複製成功率，犬隻在現階段實在無法談上普及化。」<br />\n<br />\n「我希望牠能永遠與我生活下去」<br />\n<br />\n當日前來SOOAM的，除了比利先生外還有一位來自新加坡的女士李小姐（假名）。她到訪的目的同樣是希望複製她家中的愛犬「森姆」，不過森姆仍在世。李小姐說道：「牠不只是一隻狗，牠是我的家人。雖然我現在只是想複製一隻，但若有錢的我會再複製多隻。」<br />\n<br />\n若果複製的森姆去世，會想再複製多隻嗎？<br />\n<br />\n「我不知道，但牠就有如兄弟一樣，我希望牠能永遠與我生活下去。」"},{"pid":"5f87585c09bd16d06bc02fb101dcca0ceaa0341d","tid":93568,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:52:24.000Z","msg":"就算複製都係得個樣似<br />\n有乜意義"},{"pid":"7955f7d958444836b6d3a6262a4f45d9344597ad","tid":93568,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:52:45.000Z","msg":"我想複製一個人"},{"pid":"3df4a19bfecd229d2d50985cde3112819b8019a9","tid":93568,"uid":22414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:53:33.000Z","msg":"遲d 無意中俾佢地複製返以前地球啲動物霸者咪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cab3bac282a95af5216f10308db4cf48a964fa8","tid":93568,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲d 無意中俾佢地複製返以前地球啲動物霸者咪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人類已經係動物霸者啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260a990f22217acb791193ff0ee77b61ae66f7d0","tid":93568,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>遲d 無意中俾佢地複製返以前地球啲動物霸者咪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人類已經係動物霸者啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n韓國人已經係動物霸者啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665dc981f90df8e672a3720331f23fbcca330b4e","tid":93568,"uid":44038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:01:27.000Z","msg":"我想複製一個人"},{"pid":"00044dc8db24486694102460ca6aeb4bc10b3570","tid":93568,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:13:46.000Z","msg":"複製希特拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8f25157982b8ca59be237872c8c3f2a7a34b61","tid":93568,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:15:37.000Z","msg":"幫隻狗整容咪得囉"},{"pid":"62167a4869582a5bb8fd1716ad457b9d162e2fd7","tid":93568,"uid":73404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:30:16.000Z","msg":"如果唔係美國日本都要拘泥於生命倫理 幾時會輪到韓狗做呢樣生意 佢地賣既只係自己既無道德無原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f877e2420674b5c453e4fecb086b953682d2dc9","tid":93568,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算複製都係得個樣似<br />\n有乜意義</blockquote><br />\n戲都有拍啦，複製黎比器官自己用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7e37a5be9aec541a7d87da4b4a4d07e515316a","tid":93568,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:38:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就算複製都係得個樣似<br />\n有乜意義</blockquote><br />\n戲都有拍啦，複製黎比器官自己用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢係複製已經死左既寵物"},{"pid":"80b56e68067d7ed6ee6a869782fb97e7d7092140","tid":93568,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:41:59.000Z","msg":"人類真係好中意呃鳩自己 明知整出黎只係外表一樣"},{"pid":"f97a1255fb2d5a40c7821d78f8b1ae59250b544d","tid":93568,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:08:35.000Z","msg":"同買過另一隻有咩分別？"},{"pid":"caa0c026c4c8a4b2cd862d64526833354ec5cd0c","tid":93568,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:20:51.000Z","msg":"狗體煉成"},{"pid":"27ffef3b9e4a5dfff52fbc27fa786c601de32cbb","tid":93568,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:24:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人類真係好中意呃鳩自己 明知整出黎只係外表一樣</blockquote><br />\n寵物嗰part就真係自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先撇除道唔道德，不過如果係工作犬，尤其係特別出色個啲，天生比同類更出色，好似話嗰隻嗅覺同靈敏性都比同類勁好多，咁就真係有複製價值。當然後天培唔培養得返原裝咁勁，定係會再勁啲，呢個就無得肯定，但相對成功幾會會大好多。"},{"pid":"4fd5dd4908107fbca2ce6e4cf9321cf89fe03114","tid":93568,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:33:38.000Z","msg":"個外貌一樣<br />\n但經歷同記憶點都唔同<br />\n<br />\n對飼主黎講<br />\n複製出黎果隻係替代品啫<br />\n<br />\n更何況複製技術未成熟<br />\n要搞到幾多代母犬死亡呀<br />\n一隻複製品要犧牲幾多生命？"},{"pid":"9ae1198a900be8358ce2e36d42105f6c0e76ba03","tid":93568,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T19:24:38.000Z","msg":"韓國科技勁到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd04c97502c717c300ae32c37aad43e7b0211b5c","tid":93568,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T19:32:04.000Z","msg":"多利係咪南韓起源？"},{"pid":"0c4632b05070c7af6e5d383b15b5096d421e0c2b","tid":93568,"uid":68325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T19:42:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勒曼醫院</span></span>"},{"pid":"0fc2ec3b430eaf4062e713073c213b8396da8185","tid":93568,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:09:12.000Z","msg":"ok仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632eb655e8edc04bcbe300433ee22ae9464f7ae2","tid":93568,"uid":25213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}